readme:
This is Test Package.
==================

A hubot script to send message 'Hello'

Installation
-----------------

In hubot project repo, run:

`npm install hubot-rocket-example --save`

Then add **hubot-rocket-example** to your `external-scripts.json`:

```json
["hubot-rocket-example"]
```
